    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/d467c78392c49cc1a9c59fff11afaadb.poster.avif?t=1679059179\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/d467c78392c49cc1a9c59fff11afaadb.webm?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/d467c78392c49cc1a9c59fff11afaadb.mp4?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>电力和弦是一支以团队为基础的Roguelike甲板建筑时间重置战斗，对抗Helmoth的恶魔团伙。</strong><br><br>组装地球最强大的音乐家，每个人都有自己独特的卡片和装备，要使自己的态势战斗，并摧毁足够强大的吉他来重新打开世界之间的划痕。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/bc540d2e9c15b6d721f2785121a3d3d7.poster.avif?t=1679059179\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/bc540d2e9c15b6d721f2785121a3d3d7.webm?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/bc540d2e9c15b6d721f2785121a3d3d7.mp4?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从各种各样的踢屁股字符中选择来组装乐队，每个成员都有自己独特的卡片和Playstyles。 Combo你的不同乐队成员的卡片释放出毁灭性的攻击并撕碎你的对手。尽管如此，因为如果乐队成员落在战斗中，你将失去他们并在未来的战斗中丢失他们的卡，直到你在坑停止恢复它们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/5ea779ddcbd0324ec7659c375d4df548.poster.avif?t=1679059179\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/5ea779ddcbd0324ec7659c375d4df548.webm?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/5ea779ddcbd0324ec7659c375d4df548.mp4?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当您拨打舞台到舞台时发现新卡，解锁新策略，以获取恶魔并加强销毁仪器。通过一个装满战斗，商家，随机遇到的分支路径，为治愈和恢复堕落的角色的分支路径选择您的路径。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/994870a33bfc76d094147983c477e5f9.poster.avif?t=1679059179\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/994870a33bfc76d094147983c477e5f9.webm?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724390/extras/994870a33bfc76d094147983c477e5f9.mp4?t=1679059179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
